(Эмне жанылык?)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">What&#8217;s up?</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b16f338.16122181" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b16f338.16122181','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/whats_up1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b16f338.16122181');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b16f338.16122181" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b16f338.16122181','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b16f338.16122181');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Emne boldu?<br />
(Эмне болду?)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">How are you?</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b16f5c5.73613989" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b16f5c5.73613989','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/how_are_you1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b16f5c5.73613989');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b16f5c5.73613989" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b16f5c5.73613989','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b16f5c5.73613989');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Kandaysiz?<br />
(Кандайсыз?)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Good, thanks, and you?</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b16f916.40904797" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b16f916.40904797','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/fine_thanks1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b16f916.40904797');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b16f916.40904797" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b16f916.40904797','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b16f916.40904797');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Jakshy, rahmat, ozunguz?<br />
(Жакшы, рахмат, озунуз?)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Good bye!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b16fbb1.28362023" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b16fbb1.28362023','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/good_bye1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b16fbb1.28362023');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b16fbb1.28362023" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b16fbb1.28362023','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b16fbb1.28362023');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Kosh kalyng!<br />
(Кош калын!)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">See you later!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b16fe42.29890541" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b16fe42.29890541','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/see_you_later1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b16fe42.29890541');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b16fe42.29890541" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b16fe42.29890541','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b16fe42.29890541');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Korushkoncho!<br />
