</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Small/big</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b170836.56180478" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b170836.56180478','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/small_big1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b170836.56180478');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b170836.56180478" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b170836.56180478','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b170836.56180478');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Kichine/chong<br />
(Кичине/чон)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Do you speak English?</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b170aa3.68368118" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b170aa3.68368118','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/do_you_speak_english1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b170aa3.68368118');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b170aa3.68368118" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b170aa3.68368118','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b170aa3.68368118');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Siz Anglische suyloy alasyzby?<a href="http://old.sras.org/Kyrgyz%20phrases/do%20you%20speak%20english.wav" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><br />
</a>(Сиз Англисче суйлой аласызбы?)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">I don&#8217;t speak English.</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b170d16.34527952" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b170d16.34527952','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/i_dont_speak_english1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b170d16.34527952');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b170d16.34527952" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b170d16.34527952','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b170d16.34527952');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Men Anglische suyloy albaym.<br />
(Мен англисче суйлой албайм.)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">I only speak a little Kyrgyz.</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b170f70.15417137" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b170f70.15417137','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/i_only_speak_a_little_kyrgyz1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b170f70.15417137');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b170f70.15417137" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b170f70.15417137','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b170f70.15417137');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Men bir az Kyrgyzscha suyloy alam.<br />
(Мен бир аз Кыргызсча суйлой алам.)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">I understand.</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b1711d6.04522004" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b1711d6.04522004','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/i_understand1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b1711d6.04522004');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b1711d6.04522004" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b1711d6.04522004','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b1711d6.04522004');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Men tushunom<a href="http://old.sras.org/Kyrgyz%20phrases/i%20understand.wav" target="_blank" rel="noopener">.</a><br />
(Мен тушуном.)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">I don&#8217;t understand.</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b171428.21049013" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b171428.21049013','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/i_dont_understand1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b171428.21049013');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b171428.21049013" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b171428.21049013','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b171428.21049013');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Men tushunboym<a href="http://old.sras.org/Kyrgyz%20phrases/i%20don&#039;t%20understand.wav" target="_blank" rel="noopener">.</a><br />
(Мен тушунбойм.)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Thank you!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b171678.37154910" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b171678.37154910','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/thank_you1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b171678.37154910');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b171678.37154910" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b171678.37154910','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b171678.37154910');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Rahmat!<br />
(Рахмат!)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Thank you very much!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b1718c1.80397333" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b1718c1.80397333','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/thank_you_very_much1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b1718c1.80397333');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b1718c1.80397333" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b1718c1.80397333','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b1718c1.80397333');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Chong rahmat!<br />
(Чон рахмат!)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Very well, thanks!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b171b07.94031414" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b171b07.94031414','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/very_well_thanks1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b171b07.94031414');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b171b07.94031414" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b171b07.94031414','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b171b07.94031414');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Oto jakshy, rahmat!<br />
(Ото жакшы, рахмат!)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Good</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b171d41.79788321" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b171d41.79788321','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/good1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b171d41.79788321');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b171d41.79788321" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b171d41.79788321','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b171d41.79788321');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Jakshy<br />
(Жакшы)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Please</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b171f72.86595803" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b171f72.86595803','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/please1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b171f72.86595803');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b171f72.86595803" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b171f72.86595803','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b171f72.86595803');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Suranych<br />
(Сураныч)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Please</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b1721b9.42632361" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b1721b9.42632361','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/please_21.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b1721b9.42632361');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b1721b9.42632361" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b1721b9.42632361','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b1721b9.42632361');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Otunuch<br />
(Отунуч)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">You&#8217;re welcome!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b1723f3.41609715" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b1723f3.41609715','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/you_are_welcome1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b1723f3.41609715');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b1723f3.41609715" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b1723f3.41609715','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b1723f3.41609715');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Echteke emes!<br />
(Эчтеке эмес)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Excuse me!</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b172633.49659831" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b172633.49659831','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/excuse_me1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b172633.49659831');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b172633.49659831" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b172633.49659831','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b172633.49659831');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Kechiresiz!<br />
(Кечиресиз!)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">A little</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b172855.83384111" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b172855.83384111','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/a_little1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b172855.83384111');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b172855.83384111" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b172855.83384111','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b172855.83384111');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Bir az<br />
(Бир аз)</td>
</tr>
<tr bgcolor="#ffffff">
<td align="left" valign="middle">Could you speak more slowly?</td>
<td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="sc_player_container1"><input type="button" id="btnplay_626e874b172a71.14507568" class="myButton_play" onClick="play_mp3('play','626e874b172a71.14507568','https://folkways.today/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/could_you_speak_more_slowly1-1.mp3','80','false');show_hide('play','626e874b172a71.14507568');" /><input type="button"  id="btnstop_626e874b172a71.14507568" style="display:none" class="myButton_stop" onClick="play_mp3('stop','626e874b172a71.14507568','','80','false');show_hide('stop','626e874b172a71.14507568');" /><div id="sm2-container"><!-- flash movie ends up here --></div></div></td>
<td align="left" valign="middle">Bir az jayiraak suylonguzchu!<br />
(Бир аз жайыраак суйлонузчу!)</td>
</tr>
